2
00:00:01.110 --> 00:00:01.860
What?!

3
00:00:01.860 --> 00:00:03.480
Oden, you're leaving?!

4
00:00:03.480 --> 00:00:05.740
There'll be less trouble, but we'll miss him.

5
00:00:05.740 --> 00:00:09.360
<b>Hakumai

Wano</b>

6
00:00:07.110 --> 00:00:09.360
I hear a monster lives in Kuri.

7
00:00:09.910 --> 00:00:11.910
A demon by the name of Ashura Doji.

8
00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.200
Kuri is a cancer in Wano...

9
00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:17.290
Even Shogun Sukiyaki cannot control it.

10
00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:22.460
The authorities are powerless to apprehend
criminals who take refuge in Kuri.

11
00:00:22.460 --> 00:00:26.300
But they will die there anyway
if their strength is lacking.

12
00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:31.140
Such a lawless region might
as well be another country!

13
00:00:32.930 --> 00:00:36.310
Fascinating! I shall tour the land Wano!

14
00:00:37.480 --> 00:00:39.190
Take care!

15
00:00:39.190 --> 00:00:41.350
Kin! Denjiro!

16
00:00:41.350 --> 00:00:42.730
Come visit us again!

17
00:00:42.730 --> 00:00:43.900
See you!

18
00:00:43.900 --> 00:00:47.860
He comes and goes as he pleases.

19
00:00:47.860 --> 00:00:49.650
He is a free spirit.

20
00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:51.530
Lord Yasuie!

21
00:00:51.530 --> 00:00:53.660
We have a problem!

22
00:00:54.580 --> 00:00:57.120
Look at the state of his accommodations!

23
00:00:57.120 --> 00:00:59.330
What kind of lifestyle would cause this?!

24
00:00:59.330 --> 00:01:01.870
We must charge him for the repairs!

25
00:01:03.210 --> 00:01:06.460
Or we just pretend we were
struck by a natural disaster...

26
00:01:06.460 --> 00:01:09.470
My lord, you are too soft on him!

27
00:01:09.470 --> 00:01:10.680
Lord Yasuie!

28
00:01:11.590 --> 00:01:13.220
What now?

29
00:01:15.310 --> 00:01:16.680
There is money missing?

30
00:01:16.680 --> 00:01:19.850
Yes, and I am certain
it was locked in the safe!

31
00:01:20.310 --> 00:01:21.310
Um...

32
00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:25.230
It pains me to say this...

33
00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:28.480
but I witnessed the whole thing!

34
00:01:29.820 --> 00:01:32.990
Um... Lord Oden...

35
00:01:32.990 --> 00:01:35.580
tucked the money into
his inner breast pocket...

36
00:01:36.660 --> 00:01:38.490
I knew he did it!

37
00:01:38.490 --> 00:01:40.660
He bit the hands that fed him!

38
00:01:40.660 --> 00:01:41.830
This is unforgivable!

39
00:01:41.830 --> 00:01:44.500
I think Oden would have taken it openly.

40
00:01:45.840 --> 00:01:47.380
Are you sure, Orochi?

41
00:01:48.300 --> 00:01:49.760
Y-Yes! My apologies!

42
00:01:50.170 --> 00:01:53.720
I was so scared that I couldn't stop him!

43
00:02:03.650 --> 00:02:09.070
After leaving Hakumai, Oden's group continued
to cause trouble throughout Wano

44
00:02:09.070 --> 00:02:10.940
as they headed toward Kuri.

45
00:02:18.370 --> 00:02:20.580
How long are you two going to follow me?!

46
00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:22.080
Forever!

47
00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.290
We love you so much!

48
00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:30.210
– He looks annoyed!
– He looks annoyed!

49
00:02:33.470 --> 00:02:36.550
Hey! Why are you standing out there?

50
00:02:36.550 --> 00:02:39.010
As your retainers, we must stand guard.

51
00:02:39.010 --> 00:02:40.560
Come in, you idiots!

52
00:02:40.970 --> 00:02:42.980
– Oden!
– Oden!

53
00:02:44.270 --> 00:02:45.770
What are you doing?

54
00:02:45.770 --> 00:02:47.110
I'm keeping a logbook.

55
00:02:47.520 --> 00:02:51.940
Apparently, voyagers overseas write
in them every day on their ships.

56
00:02:52.610 --> 00:02:56.320
The following are Oden's own 
words regarding his journeys.

57
00:02:59.030 --> 00:02:59.080
<b>Ringo</b>

58
00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:03.500
<b>Ringo</b>

59
00:03:07.290 --> 00:03:11.800
In Ringo, we came across
a couple of starving brothers in rags.

60
00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:11.880
<b>Izo

Son of a Former Hanayanagi

Dance School Headmaster</b>

61
00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:11.920
<b>Izo

Son of a Former Hanayanagi

Dance School Headmaster</b>
<b>Kikunojo

Izo's Younger Brother</b>

62
00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:11.960
<b>Izo

Son of a Former Hanayanagi

Dance School Headmaster</b>
<b>Kikunojo

Izo's Younger Brother</b>

63
00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:14.720
<b>Izo

Son of a Former Hanayanagi

Dance School Headmaster</b>
<b>Kikunojo

Izo's Younger Brother</b>

64
00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:16.260
Get lost!

65
00:03:20.680 --> 00:03:24.060
They were trying to earn money
by dancing, but people were cold.

66
00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:33.030
Why are you two following me?!

67
00:03:34.940 --> 00:03:36.110
Stop eating, you brats!

68
00:03:36.110 --> 00:03:37.030
I want more.

69
00:03:37.030 --> 00:03:38.530
I said stop!

70
00:03:38.530 --> 00:03:40.200
Do not give him any more!

71
00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:43.750
They mentioned being
the heirs to a school of dance,

72
00:03:43.750 --> 00:03:47.620
but their father was arrested,
breaking up their family.

73
00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:52.800
They brazenly ate our oden,
sobbing all the while.

74
00:03:59.930 --> 00:04:02.350
<b>Kibi</b>

75
00:04:01.930 --> 00:04:08.270
In Kibi, there was a ghoul who
collected hair from the living and dead alike.

76
00:04:08.770 --> 00:04:12.940
He was a freak who made a living
selling brushes made from the hair.

77
00:04:16.360 --> 00:04:16.400
<b>Kanjuro
Ghoul of Kibi</b>

78
00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.320
<b>Kanjuro
Ghoul of Kibi</b>

79
00:04:21.950 --> 00:04:25.620
Whoa! I give up! I give up! I give up!
I thought you were a corpse!

80
00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:30.040
I punched him for coming after my hair,
but then he began to follow me too.

81
00:04:30.040 --> 00:04:33.880
He claimed to have suffered—
and deservedly so—from persecution.

82
00:04:33.880 --> 00:04:43.300
<b>Udon</b>

83
00:04:34.710 --> 00:04:39.340
In the forest-covered Udon, there were
rumors of a notorious mountain bandit.

84
00:04:39.340 --> 00:04:43.470
They said women would be abducted,
and men would be beaten soundly.

85
00:04:44.930 --> 00:04:46.770
Why are you all following me?!

86
00:04:46.770 --> 00:04:48.430
You're telling me!

87
00:04:57.280 --> 00:04:59.030
Is that the mountain bandit?!

88
00:05:01.490 --> 00:05:02.160
Jump!

89
00:05:02.570 --> 00:05:04.450
Lord Oden!

