102
00:05:05.660 --> 00:05:13.540
The prodigious ninja, Raizo, quit the Kozuki Clan's
Oniwabanshu after a kunoichi broke his heart.

103
00:05:13.540 --> 00:05:17.920
I cannot live my life in hiding any longer!

104
00:05:23.260 --> 00:05:24.760
He looks annoyed...

105
00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:33.230
<b>Lawless Land of Kuri</b>

106
00:05:34.610 --> 00:05:39.780
<b>Ashura Doji
Strongest Monster in Kuri</b>

107
00:05:35.570 --> 00:05:37.940
Kozuki Oden has come to Kuri?

108
00:05:37.940 --> 00:05:40.070
He's the shogun's son!

109
00:05:40.070 --> 00:05:41.820
I wanna kill him myself!

110
00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:43.450
Catch him and bring him here!

111
00:05:43.450 --> 00:05:44.450
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

112
00:05:53.540 --> 00:05:57.750
Those in power... We hate them most of all!

113
00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.630
Where's Oden?

114
00:06:02.630 --> 00:06:04.970
He went south of here to take a dump.

115
00:06:05.300 --> 00:06:07.310
Wasn't that yesterday?

116
00:06:07.310 --> 00:06:11.680
He sometimes disappears on a whim
for one or two days, right?

117
00:06:12.390 --> 00:06:15.440
Hey, Raizo! There's a gate
to Kuri in the south!

118
00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:16.190
What?!

119
00:06:17.150 --> 00:06:22.650
Crap! I swore I'd die for him, and now
I'm late to join him on the battlefield!

