182
00:06:54.310 --> 00:06:59.190
This was a place filled with the stench
of death, blood, and violence!

183
00:06:59.190 --> 00:07:00.900
It was like a different world.

184
00:07:00.900 --> 00:07:04.610
All of their bloodlust was directed toward me!

185
00:07:05.240 --> 00:07:09.620
I'll lop off your head, Kozuki Oden!

186
00:07:19.210 --> 00:07:22.080
Open up the borderless map, then

187
00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:25.280
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

188
00:07:25.280 --> 00:07:29.670
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

189
00:07:29.670 --> 00:07:32.660
Riding on the wind

190
00:07:37.790 --> 00:07:42.000
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

191
00:07:42.190 --> 00:07:44.970
So don't you grow disheartened

192
00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:48.730
Laugh the tears away through the storm

193
00:07:48.930 --> 00:07:53.160
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

194
00:07:53.500 --> 00:07:55.760
That’s what your friends are there for

195
00:07:55.790 --> 00:07:57.920
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

196
00:07:57.920 --> 00:08:01.840
your crew will always have your back

197
00:08:02.210 --> 00:08:05.940
Even in the face of utter darkness

198
00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:08.930
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

199
00:08:09.230 --> 00:08:12.720
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

200
00:08:12.940 --> 00:08:15.710
Open up the borderless map, then

201
00:08:15.730 --> 00:08:18.570
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

202
00:08:18.870 --> 00:08:23.150
All great journeys starts with a single step

203
00:08:23.220 --> 00:08:24.160
DREAMIN’ ON

204
00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:26.940
Open up the borderless map, then

205
00:08:26.940 --> 00:08:29.680
Raise the flag we swore to defend

206
00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:32.570
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

207
00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:37.040
Just be true to yourself until the end

208
00:08:37.170 --> 00:08:41.880
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

209
00:08:55.180 --> 00:08:57.890
<b>Daimyo and Retainers</b>

210
00:08:57.890 --> 00:08:59.730
You're Kozuki Oden, huh?

211
00:09:02.310 --> 00:09:04.110
I have been disowned,

212
00:09:04.110 --> 00:09:06.030
so I no longer have a name!

213
00:09:06.650 --> 00:09:10.650
You can enter all you like,
but we kill any who try to leave!

214
00:09:10.650 --> 00:09:13.450
Especially samurai!

215
00:09:19.250 --> 00:09:21.580
It is so restrictive!

216
00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:27.170
How can anyone live in a place like this?!

217
00:09:27.630 --> 00:09:30.050
That's hilarious.

218
00:09:30.050 --> 00:09:34.300
You're never going to leave this place!

219
00:09:34.300 --> 00:09:36.430
No, don't even try to leave!

220
00:09:37.850 --> 00:09:39.730
"Don't even try to leave"?

221
00:09:39.730 --> 00:09:43.400
That is my least favorite rule!

222
00:09:43.400 --> 00:09:45.900
I make the rules here!

223
00:09:47.070 --> 00:09:48.110
Cut him down!

224
00:10:21.350 --> 00:10:22.850
That makes you the boss?

225
00:10:34.490 --> 00:10:37.410
– Oden!
– Oden!

226
00:10:37.740 --> 00:10:39.870
Oden!

227
00:10:41.700 --> 00:10:43.960
Look! The gate has been broken!

228
00:10:52.090 --> 00:10:55.510
How can an ass who grew up
pampered in the capital...

229
00:10:56.090 --> 00:10:59.350
understand what it's like to live in hell?!

230
00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:03.020
Is that all you really want to say?!

231
00:11:05.560 --> 00:11:06.520
Look!

232
00:11:07.900 --> 00:11:09.060
Up there!

233
00:11:19.370 --> 00:11:22.580
Oden! We're here to back you up!

234
00:11:26.460 --> 00:11:27.830
I must apologize.

235
00:11:28.250 --> 00:11:31.710
I seem to have finished up already.

236
00:11:32.340 --> 00:11:35.930
It took me an entire day and night.

237
00:11:45.100 --> 00:11:47.480
Kill me already!

238
00:11:47.480 --> 00:11:49.860
I know what the future holds anyway.

239
00:11:50.860 --> 00:11:52.820
I've got nothing to live for!

240
00:11:53.820 --> 00:11:58.030
This is the infamous Ashura Doji?!

241
00:11:58.570 --> 00:12:00.700
Hey, you guys!

242
00:12:01.030 --> 00:12:04.290
Do you still love me?

243
00:12:08.080 --> 00:12:11.790
Lend me your wisdom and strength!

244
00:12:12.590 --> 00:12:16.920
I have decided that the worthless scum here...

245
00:12:17.420 --> 00:12:20.050
need me as their king!

246
00:12:24.140 --> 00:12:26.930
<b>Flower

Capital</b>

247
00:12:32.690 --> 00:12:35.360
My lord, Shogun! Lord Oden is at it again!

248
00:12:35.780 --> 00:12:38.900
What? What did he do this time?!

249
00:12:39.820 --> 00:12:40.820
