626
00:13:40.670 --> 00:13:41.590
<b>Reformation 
of
 Kuri</b>

627
00:13:42.300 --> 00:13:43.970
Kin...

628
00:13:47.260 --> 00:13:49.850
You did it! Our beloved Oden did it!

629
00:13:49.850 --> 00:13:50.810
Hooray!

630
00:13:50.810 --> 00:13:52.440
You're amazing, Oden!

631
00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:54.150
You're finally Kuri's–

632
00:13:54.150 --> 00:13:55.270
Oden!

633
00:13:59.820 --> 00:14:00.990
Absolutely!

634
00:14:03.990 --> 00:14:06.830
Daimyo!

635
00:14:11.250 --> 00:14:12.750
– Lord Oden!
– Lord Oden!

636
00:14:19.210 --> 00:14:20.710
What is the matter, Ashura?

637
00:14:22.090 --> 00:14:23.470
I...

638
00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:27.720
have never seen peace before.

639
00:14:30.060 --> 00:14:32.310
Thank you, Oden!

640
00:14:32.770 --> 00:14:35.400
Stop it! You are creeping me out!

641
00:14:39.230 --> 00:14:41.490
You bastard!

642
00:14:42.900 --> 00:14:44.530
What're you doing?! Stop it!

643
00:14:44.530 --> 00:14:46.240
Hey!

644
00:14:46.240 --> 00:14:48.200
I said "Stop it"!

645
00:14:46.620 --> 00:14:48.200
Screw you!

646
00:14:49.080 --> 00:14:50.580
Knock it off already!

647
00:14:50.580 --> 00:14:53.500
Now, a daimyo requires retainers.

648
00:14:55.000 --> 00:14:58.790
Instead of surrounding myself
with the usual wise and sober men...

649
00:15:00.800 --> 00:15:03.050
I would rather have you all.

650
00:15:12.850 --> 00:15:15.940
Be my samurai!

651
00:15:35.370 --> 00:15:37.710
– Lord Oden!
– Lord Oden!

652
00:15:38.250 --> 00:15:39.380
S-S-Stop it!

653
00:15:39.380 --> 00:15:42.750
Your snot! Your snot!
It is dripping! Oh, it is on me!

654
00:15:42.750 --> 00:15:44.720
Stop it!

655
00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:52.510
Six years after that moment in time...
yet thirty-three years before the present day...

656
00:15:52.510 --> 00:15:58.350
across the world, disbanded members
of the legendary Rocks Pirates

657
00:15:58.350 --> 00:16:04.230
each formed a new crew, extended
their influence, and became infamous.

658
00:16:04.940 --> 00:16:11.030
<b>Kuri
Beach


Wano</b>

659
00:16:11.030 --> 00:16:13.790
What are they? Animals?

660
00:16:14.240 --> 00:16:16.710
Hairy humans?

661
00:16:19.170 --> 00:16:21.250
Deformed monsters?

662
00:16:28.220 --> 00:16:29.470
Did you get it?

663
00:16:29.470 --> 00:16:30.300
Yeah...

664
00:16:36.850 --> 00:16:40.770
In the distant past, many centuries ago,

665
00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:45.730
we minks and the samurai
of Wano's Kozuki Clan

666
00:16:46.490 --> 00:16:49.780
made a pledge to become sworn brothers.

667
00:16:50.360 --> 00:16:54.240
Damn! Wano is the worst!

668
00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:56.620
Dammit! Let me down!

669
00:16:58.080 --> 00:16:59.670
I'm a kappa!

670
00:16:59.670 --> 00:17:01.120
Which makes you a monster!

671
00:17:01.120 --> 00:17:03.750
I wish we'd never set sail!

672
00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:05.710
I wish we hadn't come here!

673
00:17:05.710 --> 00:17:09.010
This isn't how you treat brothers!

674
00:17:09.380 --> 00:17:12.260
A cat monster, dog monster, and a kappa...

675
00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:14.640
Is this beach cursed?

676
00:17:14.640 --> 00:17:15.970
Let's burn them alive!

677
00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:20.270
Don't do it!

678
00:17:25.150 --> 00:17:27.820
That is plenty of ingredients for today's oden...

679
00:17:35.580 --> 00:17:37.870
You wretches!

680
00:17:46.800 --> 00:17:49.840
You should all be ashamed!

681
00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:48.880
<b>Beef 
Tendon</b>

682
00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:49.010
<b>Beef 
Tendon</b>

683
00:17:49.010 --> 00:17:49.840
<b>Beef 
Tendon</b>

684
00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:53.260
You fear what is different out of ignorance!

685
00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:56.220
<b>Beef 
Tendon</b>

686
00:17:53.260 --> 00:17:56.220
It is pathetic to torment such little creatures!

687
00:17:56.810 --> 00:17:58.140
Thank you...

688
00:18:00.180 --> 00:18:01.480
Farewell.

689
00:18:01.480 --> 00:18:03.480
– Don't leave us like this!
– Don't leave us like this!

690
00:18:10.990 --> 00:18:12.990
So, who are the monsters?

691
00:18:12.990 --> 00:18:14.200
They followed me.

692
00:18:16.580 --> 00:18:19.200
<b>Inuarashi


Mink</b>

693
00:18:16.870 --> 00:18:19.120
Thank you for saving us!

694
00:18:21.250 --> 00:18:22.500
It's hot!

695
00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:26.880
Between starvation, a shipwreck,
and a violent mob, we almost died!

696
00:18:22.540 --> 00:18:26.080
<b>Neko-
mamushi


Mink</b>

697
00:18:27.880 --> 00:18:28.750
Ouch!

698
00:18:28.750 --> 00:18:31.010
Hey! This is too hot to eat!

699
00:18:31.010 --> 00:18:32.420
Whoa...

700
00:18:32.420 --> 00:18:35.720
I still can't get used to seeing animals talking.

701
00:18:38.600 --> 00:18:39.890
The minks!

702
00:18:39.890 --> 00:18:42.020
My father once told me about them.

703
00:18:42.020 --> 00:18:43.190
I thought so!

704
00:18:43.190 --> 00:18:45.810
We have that symbol in our country, too!

705
00:18:45.810 --> 00:18:48.570
You-gara and our people are brothers!

706
00:18:48.570 --> 00:18:50.190
And you saved our lives!

707
00:18:50.190 --> 00:18:51.780
We were starving...

708
00:18:51.780 --> 00:18:52.650
I see...

709
00:18:52.650 --> 00:18:54.400
Eat as much as you want.

710
00:18:54.400 --> 00:18:56.320
Here's to our savior.

711
00:18:56.320 --> 00:18:57.120
Ouch!

712
00:18:57.120 --> 00:18:58.490
Don't be shy.

713
00:18:58.490 --> 00:18:59.790
You'll like the radish.

714
00:18:59.790 --> 00:19:01.830
I won't forget this favor.

715
00:19:01.830 --> 00:19:02.330
Hot!

716
00:19:02.330 --> 00:19:04.000
Try the hanpen.

717
00:19:04.670 --> 00:19:05.250
Ouch!

718
00:19:05.250 --> 00:19:05.960
The konnyaku–

719
00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:08.460
No! It's too hot to eat!

720
00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:16.010
My tongue is sensitive like a cat's!

721
00:19:16.010 --> 00:19:18.140
Bad cat!

722
00:19:18.550 --> 00:19:20.100
Hey! Wait, Cat!

723
00:19:22.720 --> 00:19:24.230
Hey, Cat!

724
00:19:24.230 --> 00:19:26.600
Oden was meant...

725
00:19:27.730 --> 00:19:30.190
to boil!

726
00:19:32.780 --> 00:19:34.360
– That's kinda cool!
– That's kinda cool!

727
00:19:36.280 --> 00:19:37.450
Tastes good to me.

728
00:19:38.240 --> 00:19:39.620
And what are you?!

729
00:19:39.620 --> 00:19:43.080
The ship my mother and I were on sank, and...

730
00:19:44.000 --> 00:19:46.620
we were cast ashore in this country.

731
00:19:46.620 --> 00:19:49.920
We asked for help, but people threw
rocks at us for being fishmen.

732
00:19:50.340 --> 00:19:54.800
My mother got hurt, so we couldn't
go back to where we came from.

733
00:19:54.800 --> 00:19:57.180
Before my mother died, she told me,

734
00:19:57.180 --> 00:19:59.430
"Fishmen suffer discrimination...

735
00:19:59.430 --> 00:20:02.310
so claim that you're a kappa."

736
00:20:07.190 --> 00:20:09.440
I'm Kawamatsu the Kappa.

737
00:20:09.060 --> 00:20:09.100
<b>Kawamatsu

"the Kappa"</b>

738
00:20:09.100 --> 00:20:12.020
<b>Kawamatsu

"the Kappa"</b>

739
00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:11.440
I've been living off leftovers.

740
00:20:12.520 --> 00:20:17.150
Thank you for saving me
and treating me to such a delicious meal.

741
00:20:17.700 --> 00:20:19.660
I'll never forget this.

742
00:20:19.990 --> 00:20:22.450
May I eat the rest?

743
00:20:22.450 --> 00:20:25.450
Nonesense. We'll cook more,
so just wait a bit.

744
00:20:25.450 --> 00:20:28.620
No, that's not necessary. It's still edible.

745
00:20:29.960 --> 00:20:31.000
Oh no...

746
00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:33.380
I failed to express proper gratitude.

747
00:20:33.380 --> 00:20:35.880
I wasted food.

748
00:20:35.880 --> 00:20:37.590
You've grown up.

749
00:20:39.970 --> 00:20:41.720
I'm meowwy sorry, Kappa!

750
00:20:41.720 --> 00:20:43.600
I'll eat it, too!

751
00:20:45.100 --> 00:20:47.350
It's still too hot!

752
00:20:49.640 --> 00:20:51.400
What an amusing cat!

753
00:20:52.770 --> 00:20:55.860
Cat!

754
00:20:56.940 --> 00:21:01.200
There must still be creatures
out there I've never seen before.

755
00:21:01.200 --> 00:21:06.040
Meeting you all has reinvigorated
my desire to one day set sail!

756
00:21:06.040 --> 00:21:06.950
Sounds great!

757
00:21:06.950 --> 00:21:08.660
The world's a big place!

758
00:21:08.660 --> 00:21:10.460
Well then, take care!

759
00:21:13.670 --> 00:21:15.090
Let us stay here!

760
00:21:15.090 --> 00:21:16.670
Were you listening to us?!

761
00:21:16.670 --> 00:21:19.050
We have no place to go!

762
00:21:19.050 --> 00:21:22.140
All right! All right!

763
00:21:22.140 --> 00:21:22.180
All right! All right!

764
00:21:22.180 --> 00:21:22.220
All right! All right!

765
00:21:22.220 --> 00:21:22.260
All right! All right!

766
00:21:22.260 --> 00:21:22.300
All right! All right!

767
00:21:22.300 --> 00:21:22.340
All right! All right!

768
00:21:22.340 --> 00:21:22.390
All right! All right!

769
00:21:22.390 --> 00:21:22.430
All right! All right!

770
00:21:22.430 --> 00:21:22.470
All right! All right!

771
00:21:22.470 --> 00:21:22.510
All right! All right!

772
00:21:22.510 --> 00:21:22.550
All right! All right!

773
00:21:22.550 --> 00:21:22.590
All right! All right!

774
00:21:22.590 --> 00:21:22.640
All right! All right!

775
00:21:22.640 --> 00:21:22.680
All right! All right!

776
00:21:23.350 --> 00:21:25.140
Yay!

777
00:21:26.010 --> 00:21:27.270
We got more people...

778
00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:30.310
I guess you just can't reject anyone.

779
00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:34.560
That's fine and all, but we're in a bind here.

780
00:21:34.560 --> 00:21:37.570
You lent money to Orochi
without asking me again!

781
00:21:37.570 --> 00:21:39.440
Why would you help that creep?!

782
00:21:39.440 --> 00:21:40.320
You see...

783
00:21:40.320 --> 00:21:45.080
He may be independent now, but with
his ties to Yasuie, I cannot abandon him.

784
00:21:49.910 --> 00:21:53.170
Silent steps. Stealthy steps. Ninja steps.

785
00:21:53.170 --> 00:21:55.590
Understood? These are the fundamentals.

786
00:21:55.590 --> 00:21:56.750
– Okay!
– Okay!

787
00:21:56.750 --> 00:21:57.750
Let's go!

788
00:21:57.750 --> 00:21:59.630
Don't be afraid of Yasuie!

789
00:21:59.630 --> 00:22:02.970
Silent steps. Stealthy steps. Ninja steps.

790
00:21:59.630 --> 00:22:07.010
<b>Hakumai</b>

791
00:22:02.970 --> 00:22:05.930
– Silent steps. Stealthy steps. Ninja steps.
– Silent steps. Stealthy steps. Ninja steps.

792
00:22:11.140 --> 00:22:14.020
Why would you want to 
steal this much money?

793
00:22:14.020 --> 00:22:16.440
Lord Oden was broke!

794
00:22:16.440 --> 00:22:19.730
If you're gonna kill us,
just do it already, you hedgehog!

795
00:22:19.730 --> 00:22:22.900
If it'll help Lord Oden...

796
00:22:22.900 --> 00:22:26.160
I'm happy to die!

797
00:22:27.580 --> 00:22:31.750
Damn you, Oden. You certainly
know how to pick them.

798
00:22:33.870 --> 00:22:36.380
I am giving you the money
you tried to steal.

799
00:22:37.790 --> 00:22:38.550
– What?!
– What?!

800
00:22:38.550 --> 00:22:42.220
Lord Yasuie! These are Hakumai's funds!

801
00:22:42.220 --> 00:22:43.510
And...?

802
00:22:47.550 --> 00:22:50.470
You can have this too. It is yours!

803
00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:52.180
Even more money?!

804
00:22:52.180 --> 00:22:54.730
You gotta be kidding me! Is this a trap?!

805
00:22:55.980 --> 00:22:57.440
Do you love Oden?

806
00:22:59.650 --> 00:23:08.870
Then take this money, make yourselves presentable,
learn some manners, buy some books, and study!

807
00:23:10.290 --> 00:23:12.040
These don't suit us!

808
00:23:19.420 --> 00:23:20.460
I am...

809
00:23:20.460 --> 00:23:22.340
No! Speak from your stomach!

810
00:23:22.340 --> 00:23:23.510
I am...!

